text: Always GOOD...ALWAYS FRESH!  This place is AMAZING!  5 STARS!

text: Tried Papa Murphy's for the first time based on the great reviews and was not disappointed. You choose the type of pizza crust and toppings and they make it right there for you. The process is quick and the staff were very helpful and ‚Ä¶More

text: Papa Murphy's is a Friday tradition in our house going back to when I was a child in California. I'm so glad these guys have moved in close to my home in Virginia! I have never had a bad experience here. The staff is friendly, helpful, and ‚Ä¶More

text: Papa Murphy's *never* disappoints & the employees ROCK!! Love this place!

name: Laurie Ulbricht
text: The first time we tried it, we were hooked.  We have never been dissapointed with any of the Pizzas we've had.  The staff has always been very helpful and friendly.  I order online and pick it up on my way home making my night easy.  Clean ‚Ä¶More

name: G Land
text: Their pizza concept is different, they make it fresh right there in front of you you take it home and bake it yourself, so it's freshly made freshly cooked.  All the pizza's we have tried so far been very delicious!!

name: Scott Stallings
text: This place has very high quality pizza at reasonable prices. The staff is very friendly and pleasant. The ingredients are top notch. My personal favorites are the garlic herb chicken, the meat lovers, and the Hawaiian. They also run a lot of specials like $10 Tuesdays for large pizzas. Give them a try, you won't be disappointed.

name: Laura Boire
text: One of the best take and bake pizzas i have ever had. The pizza was ready when i arrive and had all instructions included.  I found that i like it more than the other poppa pizza place.

name: Jennifer Hardison
text: Always great pizza and great service. Sign up for the emails and texts and get coupons. They also have a military discount!

name: kim angel
text: First time trying it and it was amazing. Definitely no excuse to get grocery store frozen pizza over this, also nice when you don‚Äôt what to buy all the ingredients to make a pizza at home, and won‚Äôt break your budget

name: Shannon Renfro
text: Amazing quality, fast, and love that they honor military with a special discount. Their deep dish Chicago style is the best I have found in this area (except the sauce is still under the cheese). We will be making this a weekly treat!

name: Maureen McCormick
text: Great pizza, made just the way you want it!

name: Adam Przekop
text: Best pizza in the area and super friendly and helpfull crew. Highly recommended!

name: Raymond and Margie Stallings
text: Papa Murphy's Pizza is a great concept.  You order your pizza then watch them make it. They wrap it and you take it home to bake it.  They are very generous with their toppings and it is delicious!  I like the fact that I can bake it when we're ready to eat it!  The staff is very friendly too with great customer service!

name: m zerf
text: Was very happy to find this franchise had the same style experience and friendly people as the one back home in South Dakota! Will be back to this one often!

name: N K
text: A huge fan of this change since we were in the Rockies. Love the Tuesday deal to an extent where pizza Tuesday is more frequent for me than taco Tuesday. The staff at this particular location is extremely helpful and quick.

name: ashley bannon
text: The customer service at Papa Murphy's is outstanding. I have a three month old in a car seat and both times I have went the employees have helped me carry my pizza to car so I could carry him. The pizza is very tasty and the service is excellent! Great place!

name: Terrie Smith
text: Started out trying to order online...website not so great! But they made up for it in service and fresh ingredients. We've had it before but tonight was the best one yet. We like to do a half his fav and half my fav. The guy made it to order quickly!  We will be back soon. Great job all!!

name: Angela Holden
text: Always fast, friendly good

text:
Good take n bake pizza. $10 Tuesday deal. Easy order on line
and pick up. Nice!

name: Erik Bergquist
text: Very friendly and lovely staff. Great pricing. Great for friday pizza night, with their $5 Favs you can really let your creativity sore.

name: Doris Scott
text: Great set up took 10 minutes to order pay and leave haven't tasted it yet but smells bangin

name: Anthony Fields
text: This is our new pizza place, we love the quality and taste of the pizza here. Always fresh ingredients and the staff is awesome.

name: Zach burgess
text: Papa Murphy's tastes soooo great! The staff is very polite, and the toppings are so fresh! Try it, you will never have papa johns, or pizza hut ever again!

name: Ryan Katuzienski
text: Some of the best take and bake pizza around and very friendly staff especially Matt.

name: Andrew Ball
text: Ruthlessly efficient staff and great customer service. Outstanding overall. Phenomenal value.

name: faressa slaughter
text: Every since my first time going to Papa Murphy's I have not been able to imagine going anywhere else. The prices are very reasonable, and the  ingredients are fresh. You have to try it to see what I mean.

name: Calvin Cooper
text: They close at 9pm, went by at 8:58pm and lights out closed. I know it's only 2 minuyes but business is business. Was really looking forward to trying this place for the first time, we were in the area and last minute decision.
